itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:12:23.000Z","msg":"车公灵签第九十二签 (中签)<br />\n车公灵签第九十二签：签文<br />\n人生何在逞英豪，天理人情只要公；天眼恢恢疏不漏，定然作福福来纵。<br />\n<br />\n车公灵签第九十二签：解签<br />\n家宅平平 作福加增 自身平安 婚姻成合<br />\n<br />\n车公灵签第九十二签：断签<br />\n家宅装风光 占病作福 自身不吉 出入不安 婚姻不合 求财无 外强中干 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有私无公 上天示警 不然灾星</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"好簽"},{"pid":"a48c4115f049fb21d0ebddf10c18e6f5afd7e58a","tid":1842732,"uid":289733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"天理人情只要公；天眼恢恢疏不漏<br />\n<br />\n車公都話要獨立調查委員會， 彰顯公道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379f8f9bed7bff7dd22387a7afcbc684863974b1","tid":1842732,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>拒絕迷信啦</strong>"},{"pid":"5c744c235f475b7d66800c6da015f39933950881","tid":1842732,"uid":271807,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"我試解<br />\n<br />\n人生何在逞英豪<br />\n指有人為咗刷鞋做咗好多事<br />\n<br />\n天理人情只要公<br />\n指世事萬物都離不開公道<br />\n<br />\n天眼恢恢疏不漏<br />\n指人在做、天在看，人做咗不公之事始終會有制裁<br />\n<br />\n定然作福福來縱<br />\n指做公義之事，終會功成"},{"pid":"e8b2c9bcad311c93938e14f6ca24df4644c90e5b","tid":1842732,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"唔係冇下簽架咩 中其實即係下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2cabd2c11d711c286e6878a83cc0c53586cd38","tid":1842732,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"人生何事充英豪"},{"pid":"da3c17282d4da147a5cc689803dbc061150c413f","tid":1842732,"uid":8186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re